{"tid":1556171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各位比狗追時 唔好掛住跑 身邊好多人要救","createTime":"2019-09-09T15:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T04:30:54.000Z","uid":40856,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c5637f1400fc21d898bd4f87ede07227ec0fc3a2","tid":1556171,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"星期六係東涌 班狗湧埋欄杆位<br />\n因為大家都幾乎夾死<br />\n我一個人扶住個呀伯走 所以行得比較慢<br />\n當時好多手足好驚 不斷撞我同呀伯<br />\n最近既速龍距離我得十米到<br />\n呀伯叫我唔好扶 照顧自己先<br />\n結果我狗急跳牆 跳欄落山坡之際 扭到膝頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己而家拐足兩日 <br />\n當時我走甩左向上望 <br />\n望到伯伯比狗圍住 但仲屌緊狗阻佢等巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw雖然大家都好驚比狗拉 走係無可厚非<br />\n但望一望身邊既人 好多都走唔快 行動不便<br />\n女又好 老野又好 拖左佢地走先 唔好怕羞<br />\n萬一不幸有手足比狗捉到 <br />\n情況許可希望大家一齊大膽少少 主動救人<br />\n<br />\n利申：我weak 尋日只係係屋企做冷氣軍師 冇同各位作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9eac9a39a0ff8261ec864f92d7005955737e0a","tid":1556171,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:30:56.000Z","msg":"天地有正氣 呀伯我愛你！"},{"pid":"088ea596efdd64ab4a41fe0132764d3667acf1fb","tid":1556171,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5c2bfa473441ade489abf32d4551bd158621cbc5","tid":1556171,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"香港人幾時先肯覺醒 根本個個都係Condom<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555687</a>"},{"pid":"30f9d6d42d6aa65ca51239bcec4578a26576165f","tid":1556171,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:31:35.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5813ba64f06cf5b66dd86d36fc44bda0ee60ca06","tid":1556171,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:31:48.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9743c9c508e02f5ef117a18b0643c3